== Fossil ==

Fossil is a distributed version control system, bug tracking system and wiki software (DVCS, DBTS, DWIKI).

Read more:
* http://www.fossil-scm.org - home page.
* http://www.fossil-scm.org/index.html/doc/tip/www/stats.wiki - performance.
* http://www.fossil-scm.org/index.html/doc/tip/www/quickstart.wiki - quickstart.
* http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fossil_%28software%29 - Wikipedia article.

Fossil currently not supported by [[VC]], but job in progress - http://www.mail-archive.com/fossil-users@lists.fossil-scm.org/msg00742.html

A fossil repository for vc-fossil.el to use [[VC]] is here: http://chiselapp.com/user/venks/repository/emacs-fossil
Login as anonymous to download.

----
alternately, download vc-fossil from MELPA.
